            <title>[MAHOUT-1352] Option to change RecommenderJob output format</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-1352</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Can we add an option to output a SequenceFile? I hard coded it to allow the Solr-recommender to work with the output file but it is probably best put in an option.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;      //extract out the recommendations&lt;br/&gt;
     Job aggregateAndRecommend = prepareJob(&lt;br/&gt;
             new Path(aggregateAndRecommendInput), outputPath, SequenceFileInputFormat.class,&lt;br/&gt;
             PartialMultiplyMapper.class, VarLongWritable.class, PrefAndSimilarityColumnWritable.class,&lt;br/&gt;
             AggregateAndRecommendReducer.class, VarLongWritable.class, RecommendedItemsWritable.class,&lt;br/&gt;
             SequenceFileOutputFormat.class); &amp;lt;-- text format in Mahout trunk&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Should be able to choose format class from the params.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
